<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Ernest & Rosemary Wedding</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

html{
scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
font-family: "Georgia", serif;
background:#f3eee8;
color:#111;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

.hidden{
display:none;
}

.screen{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}

.hero-title{
font-size:4rem;
font-style:italic;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.subtitle{
font-size:1.1rem;
margin-bottom:25px;
}

.envelope{
width:320px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:0.3s ease;
}

.envelope:hover{
transform:scale(1.03);
}

.main-hero{
height:85vh;
background:url('YOUR_MAIN_COUPLE_IMAGE_HERE') center/cover no-repeat;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
color:white;
position:relative;
}

.overlay{
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
position:absolute;
top:0;
left:0;
width:100%;
height:100%;
}

.hero-content{
position:relative;
z-index:2;
}

.hero-content h1{
font-size:5rem;
font-style:italic;
}

.hero-content p{
font-size:1.3rem;
margin-top:15px;
}

.section{
padding:90px 20px;
max-width:1150px;
margin:auto;
text-align:center;
}

.section-title{
font-size:3rem;
font-style:italic;
margin-bottom:35px;
}

.story{
max-width:850px;
margin:auto;
line-height:1.9;
font-size:1.1rem;
}

.cards{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:25px;
margin-top:45px;
}

.card{
background:white;
padding:30px;
border-radius:15px;
box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.card h3{
margin-bottom:15px;
font-size:1.5rem;
}

.gallery{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));
gap:20px;
margin-top:40px;
}

.gallery img{
width:100%;
border-radius:10px;
object-fit:cover;
height:350px;
}

.button{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:20px;
padding:14px 28px;
background:#6c4ca4;
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
border-radius:50px;
transition:0.3s ease;
}

.button:hover{
opacity:0.9;
}

.footer{
padding:70px 20px;
text-align:center;
font-size:1rem;
}

.quote{
font-style:italic;
font-size:1.2rem;
margin-top:30px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero-title{
font-size:2.5rem;
}

.hero-content h1{
font-size:2.8rem;
}

.section-title{
font-size:2.2rem;
}

.gallery img{
height:260px;
}

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- SCREEN 1 -->

<section class="screen" id="screen1">

<h1 class="hero-title">Ernest & Rosemary</h1>

<p class="subtitle">(Tap on the envelope to open!)</p>

<img 
class="envelope"
id="openEnvelope"
src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/561/561127.png"
alt="Envelope">

</section>

<!-- SCREEN 2 -->

<section class="screen hidden" id="screen2">

<h1 class="hero-title">You're Invited</h1>

<p class="subtitle">to the wedding!</p>

<img 
class="envelope"
id="openInvite"
src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2099/2099199.png"
alt="Invitation">

<p style="margin-top:20px;">
(Click on the letter to proceed!)
</p>

</section>

<!-- MAIN WEBSITE -->

<div id="website" class="hidden">

<section class="main-hero">

<div class="overlay"></div>

<div class="hero-content">
<h1>Ernest & Rosemary</h1>
<p>October 23, 2027 • Tampa, Florida</p>
</div>

</section>

<!-- OUR STORY -->

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>

<p class="story">

Ernest and I met in 2020 through mutual friends, and what started simply quickly turned into something real. By 2021, we had made it official, and from that moment on, everything just felt right.

We’ve grown through so much together, learning, evolving, and choosing each other every step of the way while keeping God at the center of it all.

In November 2025, Ernest planned the most beautiful proposal surrounded by family and loved ones, and of course, I said yes.

Our story is full of love, growth, laughter, and real moments. This is only the beginning for us.

</p>

<p class="quote">
“Therefore what God has joined together, let no one separate.”
<br>
Mark 10:9
</p>

</section>

<!-- DETAILS -->

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">Wedding Details</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">

<h3>Ceremony</h3>

<p>St. Mark Evangelist Catholic Church</p>

<p>October 23, 2027</p>

<p>3:30 PM</p>

<a href="#" class="button">View Map</a>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>Reception</h3>

<p>The Venetian Event Center</p>

<p>October 23, 2027</p>

<p>6:00 PM</p>

<a href="#" class="button">View Map</a>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- TIMELINE -->

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">Timeline</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>1:00 PM</h3>
<p>Ceremony Begins</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>5:30 PM</h3>
<p>Cocktail Hour</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>6:00 PM</h3>
<p>Reception Begins</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>8:30 PM</h3>
<p>Dancing & Celebration</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- GALLERY -->

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">Gallery</h2>

<div class="gallery">

<img src="YOUR_IMAGE_1_HERE">

<img src="YOUR_IMAGE_2_HERE">

<img src="YOUR_IMAGE_3_HERE">

<img src="YOUR_IMAGE_4_HERE">

</div>

</section>

<!-- DRESS CODE -->

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">Dress Code</h2>

<p class="story">

Guests are invited to dress elegantly in attire of their choice paired with our designated wedding accessories.

Ladies: Olive Green Gele/Head Tie

Gentlemen: Olive Green Fila/Cap

Please contact Rosemary for ordering details.

</p>

</section>

<!-- RSVP -->

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">RSVP</h2>

<p class="story">

We would love to celebrate this special day with you.

Please confirm your attendance by May 15, 2027.

</p>

<a href="#" class="button">RSVP HERE</a>

</section>

<!-- REGISTRY -->

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">Registry</h2>

<p class="story">

Your presence is truly the greatest gift to us.

For those who would like to give, gifts are welcome on the day of the celebration.

</p>

<a href="#" class="button">View Registry</a>

</section>

<!-- CULTURE -->

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">Our Culture</h2>

<p class="story">

Our love story is also about where we come from.

We are proud to celebrate our Nigerian heritage through tradition, music, family, and culture.

Both our church wedding and traditional ceremony will take place on the same day.

</p>

</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->

<section class="footer">

<p>Thank you for being part of our story.</p>

<br>

<p>#RNE2027</p>

</section>

</div>

<script>

const screen1 = document.getElementById('screen1');
const screen2 = document.getElementById('screen2');
const website = document.getElementById('website');

document.getElementById('openEnvelope').onclick = function(){

screen1.classList.add('hidden');

screen2.classList.remove('hidden');

}

document.getElementById('openInvite').onclick = function(){

screen2.classList.add('hidden');

website.classList.remove('hidden');

window.scrollTo(0,0);

}

</script>

</body>
</html>
